## Intensity Pattern

### Mono

Compare intensity to grey matter.

[**T1**]{.blue}

-   **Hypo T1:** fluid (chronic lesion)

-   **Hyper T1:** 
    -   Fat (except `T1FS`)
    -   Protein (depend on content)
    -   Blood (early & late subacute)
    -   Paramagnetic, Melanin

[**T2**]{.blue}

-   **Hyper T2:** fluid (CSF) > fat   


### Combined


-   **Hypo T1 & T2:** Air, Flow void (high-flow vessel), Calcification



-   **Iso T1 & T2:** Muscle




-   **Hypo T1 + Hyper T2:** fluid





